            <lg xml:id="TK71">
<l>aṉpiṟku muṇṭō vaṭaikkuntā ḻārvalar</l>
<l>puṉkaṇīr pūca ṟarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there any bolt at all can shut in love? the tears of grief</l>
<l>of those who love betray their turmoil.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
